Summary: Cigar shape object seen in photo after downloading into computer.
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile taking pictures of the evening sky, a cigar shape object appeared after dowloading. A similar object was seen on February 25th and reported at the MUFON site. We have several pictures of the same shape taken on different days.
